[lyottia_conversation_19_goblin_main_first]
{
	[text*]
	{
		screen_text = "Ah, the hero of our age! Do not be modest my friend, you single-handedly smashed this base to pieces. A base that has been resisting the foul magic of liches and lithids since its blueprints were first drawn. A base that consumed large part of goblin society for too long. And the purpose? To surprise the human and dwarven kingdoms with a devastating attack? To conquer the land? What good would that bring? It wouldn't bring any good even to us, goblins. We're the happiest when we're constructing new inventions and exploding with them. We need to remember that. And I will make sure that Cagoblia does not forget it again for a long time. But you don't have time to spare. We have our machinery to carry us to safety quickly, but you need to walk on foot. And it won't be long until the dark wizardry creatures of this swarm pounce at this place. Make it to the exit. It will take some walk, but you'll get out of the swamp. There's a human fortification there, called Gloomwall fortress. I'm sure you'll appreciate reconcilliating with you fellow humans after the terrible company this swamp has to offer.";
	  f scroll_rate = 10.000000;
	}
}
[lyottia_conversation_19_goblin_main_next]
{
	[text*]
	{
		screen_text = "We'll get ourselves to safety with our machinery. I hope you'll make it out safe, too. The liches are sure to tear this place to pieces.";
	  f scroll_rate = 10.000000;
	}
}
[lyottia_conversation_19_goblin_npc_1_first]
{
	[text*]
	{
		screen_text = "Hello, grand traveler. You're the one who destroyed our entire machinery! Thank you. I was getting so annoyed of constructing the kill bots that I intentionally damaged their legs. They were meant to chase survivors of destroyed cities. Can you imagine the looks on faces of refugees and our generals if all kill bots suddenly fell to ground with legs broken?";
	  f scroll_rate = 10.000000;
	}
}
[lyottia_conversation_19_goblin_npc_1_next]
{
	[text*]
	{
		screen_text = "Now that this nonsensical military operation is over, I will be able to work on inventions are actually useful. I currently hope to create a machine that would wash clothes automatically. I might call it the washing machine.";
	  f scroll_rate = 10.000000;
	}
}
[lyottia_conversation_19_goblin_npc_2_first]
