	[text*]
	{
		choice = shop;
		screen_text = "A customer! A customer! After all these years, finally a friendly faces has approached our base. Please, buy, sell, exchange to your liking. I have been the butt of everyone's jokes since we started building this base, but finally, FINALLY, my shop has a customer. Geggetti, Ritaz, Kertz, Vaddinoss, ... they can all go to hell now! Well, I guess they already are there, since you have slain them. Well...no real pity. Hope they suffered a lot. They would always barter with those hideous barter'o'mats instead of visiting my cosy store. Here, see my collection!";
